summary: Performance friendly ENB that uses version 0.119
descriptionHtml:
Uses [url=http://enbdev.com/mod_tesskyrim_v0119.htm]ENB Version 0.119[/url]
-=FPS cost for [b]me[/b]=-
9 fps loss indoors
10 fps loss outdoors
[color=#ff0000]This will be different for everyone depending on their ini file or specs[/color]


[color=#ffff00]-=Installation=-[/color]
1. Put all files except the important folder in Skyrim directory
2. Select one of the options inside the important folder
3. Put them in Skyrim directory
[color=#ffff00]-=HialgoBoost=-[/color]
1. Download & Install [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/15123/?]HiAlgoBoost[/url]
2. Rename HiAlgo's d3d9.dll to d3d9_hialgo.dll
3. Open enbseries.ini and set EnableProxyLibrary=false to true
[color=#ffff00]-=SweetFX=-[/color]
1. Open HiAlgoBoost.ini
2. Set EnableProxy_d3d9 = false to true
3. Set ProxyLibrary_d3d9 = (your sweetfx name).dll

-=Specs=-
AMD Radeon HD 7000 series
Intel(R) Core(TM)2 Duo CPU E8400 @ 3.00GHz 2.99 GHz
4 GB RAM
64-bit Operating system
author: Mirrorizen
